  "home_intro_html": "<nav class=\"category-nav\" aria-label=\"코스 카테고리\" style=\"margin: 24px 0; padding: 20px; background: var(--surface, #fffdfa); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border, #e8ddc9);\">\n  <h3 style=\"font-size: 14px; color: var(--brand, #1a3558); margin: 0 0 12px; letter-spacing: 0.02em;\">📚 카테고리별 보기</h3>\n  <ul style=\"list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px;\">\n    <li><a href=\"#course-claude-autowork\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:6px 14px; background:#f5efe0; color:#1a3558; border-radius:999px; text-decoration:none; font-size:13px; font-weight:500;\">Claude 자동화</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"#course-claude-content-engine\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:6px 14px; background:#f5efe0; color:#1a3558; border-radius:999px; text-decoration:none; font-size:13px; font-weight:500;\">콘텐츠 엔진</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"#course-claude-sop\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:6px 14px; background:#f5efe0; color:#1a3558; border-radius:999px; text-decoration:none; font-size:13px; font-weight:500;\">1인 사업가 SOP</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"#course-claude-intro-email\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:6px 14px; background:#f5efe0; color:#1a3558; border-radius:999px; text-decoration:none; font-size:13px; font-weight:500;\">이메일 자동화</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"#course-claude-monthly-revenue\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:6px 14px; background:#f5efe0; color:#1a3558; border-radius:999px; text-decoration:none; font-size:13px; font-weight:500;\">매출 분석</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"#course-claude-customer-script\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:6px 14px; background:#f5efe0; color:#1a3558; border-radius:999px; text-decoration:none; font-size:13px; font-weight:500;\">고객 응대</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"#course-claude-launchpad\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:6px 14px; background:#f5efe0; color:#1a3558; border-radius:999px; text-decoration:none; font-size:13px; font-weight:500;\">서비스 런칭</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"#course-deepwork-1hr\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:6px 14px; background:#f5efe0; color:#1a3558; border-radius:999px; text-decoration:none; font-size:13px; font-weight:500;\">딥워크·생산성</a></li>\n  </ul>\n</nav>\n<div style=\"background: var(--bg); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); margin-bottom: 0;\">\n  <div class=\"wrap\" id=\"courses\" style=\"padding: 56px 0 48px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 40px;\">\n\n    <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;\">\n      <span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;\">Courses</span>\n      <h2 style=\"font-size: clamp(20px, 2.8vw, 26px); font-weight: 700; color: var(--fg); margin: 0; letter-spacing: -0.015em;\">지금 열린 코스</h2>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); margin: 0; line-height: 1.65;\">각 코스는 독립적으로 수강할 수 있으며, 순서대로 따라가면 더 탄탄히 쌓입니다.</p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px;\">\n\n      <a href=\"/claude-bizflow\" style=\"text-decoration: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; background: #FFFFFF; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius-card); overflow: hidden; transition: box-shadow 0.18s;\" title=\"Claude로 만드는 1인 사업 자동화\">\n        <div style=\"background: var(--soft); padding: 28px 24px 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);\">\n          <span style=\"display: inline-block; background: var(--brand); color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 99px; width: fit-content; letter-spacing: 0.04em;\">시리즈 1</span>\n          <h3 style=\"font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--fg); margin: 0; line-height: 1.35; letter-spacing: -0.01em;\">Claude로 만드는<br>1인 사업 자동화</h3>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"padding: 20px 24px 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; flex: 1;\">\n          <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin: 0; line-height: 1.65;\">반복 업무를 AI 워크플로우로 대체하는 8차시 실습 과정. 도구 없이 Claude 하나로 시작합니다.</p>\n          <div style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px;\">\n            <span style=\"font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); background: var(--soft); padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 99px;\">8차시</span>\n            <span style=\"font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); background: var(--soft); padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 99px;\">자동화</span>\n            <span style=\"font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); background: var(--soft); padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 99px;\">워크플로우</span>\n          </div>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--brand); margin-top: auto;\">수강하기 →</span>\n        </div>\n      </a>\n\n      <a href=\"/claude-sop\" style=\"text-decoration: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; background: #FFFFFF; border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius-card); overflow: hidden; transition: box-shadow 0.18s;\" title=\"Claude 워크플로우 SOP 만들기\">\n        <div style=\"background: var(--soft); padding: 28px 24px 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);\">\n          <span style=\"display: inline-block; background: var(--brand-2); color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 99px; width: fit-content; letter-spacing: 0.04em;\">시리즈 2</span>\n          <h3 style=\"font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--fg); margin: 0; line-height: 1.35; letter-spacing: -0.01em;\">Claude 워크플로우<br>SOP 만들기</h3>\n        </div>\n        <div style=\"padding: 20px 24px 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; flex: 1;\">\n          <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin: 0; line-height: 1.65;\">인수인계·외주에 바로 쓸 수 있는 재사용 프롬프트 문서를 직접 만들어보는 실습 과정.</p>\n          <div style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px;\">\n            <span style=\"font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); background: var(--soft); padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 99px;\">SOP</span>\n            <span style=\"font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); background: var(--soft); padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 99px;\">프롬프트 문서</span>\n            <span style=\"font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); background: var(--soft); padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 99px;\">재사용</span>\n          </div>\n          <span style=\"font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--brand); margin-top: auto;\">수강하기 →</span>\n        </div>\n      </a>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <div style=\"background: var(--soft); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius-card); padding: 32px 36px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px;\">\n      <div style=\"display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px;\">\n        <h2 style=\"font-size: clamp(17px, 2.2vw, 20px); font-weight: 700; color: var(--fg); margin: 0; letter-spacing: -0.015em;\">코어 캠퍼스는 이런 곳입니다</h2>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 560px;\">화려한 커리큘럼보다 실제로 쓸 수 있는 것을 먼저 생각합니다. 1인 사업가가 혼자서 반복 업무를 줄이고, 구조 있는 일 방식을 만들어가도록 설계했습니다.</p>\n      </div>\n      <ul style=\"list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;\">\n        <li style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--fg); line-height: 1.55;\">\n          <span style=\"color: var(--brand); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px;\">·</span>\n          <span>15분 단위로 설계해 바쁜 일정에도 진도를 낼 수 있습니다.</span>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--fg); line-height: 1.55;\">\n          <span style=\"color: var(--brand); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px;\">·</span>\n          <span>별도 개발 지식 없이, Claude 하나만으로 실습할 수 있습니다.</span>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--fg); line-height: 1.55;\">\n          <span style=\"color: var(--brand); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px;\">·</span>\n          <span>각 코스는 독립적으로 완결되며, 시리즈로 이어지면 더 탄탄해집니다.</span>\n        </li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>",
  "site_headline": "핵심만 파는 AI 실습 강의",
  "footer_html": "<div style=\"padding: 8px 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); margin: 0;\">코어 캠퍼스 · 핵심을 다지는 AI 실무 강의</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin: 0; opacity: 0.7;\">질문이나 피드백은 각 코스 페이지 하단을 이용해 주세요.</p>\n</div>",
  "hero_html": "<div class=\"wrap\" style=\"max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:72px 40px 80px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 420px;gap:56px;align-items:center;background:var(--bg,#FBF8F3)\">\n  <div>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent,#B8860B);margin:0 0 20px\">Core Campus · AI 기획 코스</p>\n    <h1 style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(36px,4.5vw,58px);font-weight:800;line-height:1.15;color:var(--fg,#1A1814);margin:0 0 24px;letter-spacing:-0.02em\">Claude로 완성하는<br><em style=\"font-style:normal;color:var(--brand,#3D2F1E)\">1인 사업가<br>유튜브 기획</em></h1>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;color:#4A4540;max-width:480px;margin:0 0 36px\">아이디어 발굴부터 스크립트 완성까지. Claude를 기획 파트너로 삼아 꾸준히 올릴 수 있는 유튜브 시스템을 만드는 실전 코스입니다.</p>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap\">\n      <a href=\"#enroll\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:14px 32px;background:var(--brand,#3D2F1E);color:#FFFDF9;font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.01em\">수강 신청하기</a>\n      <a href=\"#curriculum\" style=\"display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--brand,#3D2F1E);text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid var(--accent,#B8860B);padding-bottom:2px\">커리큘럼 보기 →</a>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;gap:32px;margin-top:44px;padding-top:36px;border-top:1px solid #E6DDD0\">\n      <div>\n        <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:800;color:var(--fg,#1A1814);margin:0 0 4px\">8주</p>\n        <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#7A6F65;margin:0;letter-spacing:0.05em\">완성 커리큘럼</p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"width:1px;background:#E6DDD0\"></div>\n      <div>\n        <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:800;color:var(--fg,#1A1814);margin:0 0 4px\">32개</p>\n        <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#7A6F65;margin:0;letter-spacing:0.05em\">실전 프롬프트</p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"width:1px;background:#E6DDD0\"></div>\n      <div>\n        <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:800;color:var(--fg,#1A1814);margin:0 0 4px\">평생</p>\n        <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#7A6F65;margin:0;letter-spacing:0.05em\">수강 권한</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <figure style=\"margin:0;position:relative\">\n    <img src=\"/assets/placeholder/hero-editorial.svg\" alt=\"유튜브 기획 워크플로우 일러스트\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:12px;display:block;aspect-ratio:4/5;object-fit:cover\" />\n    <figcaption style=\"position:absolute;bottom:20px;left:20px;right:20px;background:rgba(251,248,243,0.92);backdrop-filter:blur(6px);padding:14px 18px;border-radius:8px;border-left:3px solid var(--accent,#B8860B)\">\n      <p style=\"font-family:'Pretendard',system-ui,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;color:#3D2F1E;margin:0\"><strong style=\"font-weight:700\">\"기획이 막혔던 사람이</strong> 매주 1편을 올리게 됐습니다.\"</p>\n    </figcaption>\n  </figure>\n</div>",
  "site_tagline_top": "AI × 1인 사업가를 위한 실습 강의"
}